0.2.1{
+Data retrieval functions are now properly asynchronous, using a callback system
+Reverted from uws back to bufferutil (dependencies) because I believe it is causing some issues. If these persist this will be undone
}
0.2.0{
+Updated the libraries the bot is built on, should fix the disconnection issues
+Added a restart command
+Installed prerequisites on the host machine necessary for voice connectivity, should it be needed in the future
+Added functions for saving and retrieving server data in JSON format, and test functions to verify their functionality
}
